lead_paragraph: Alastair Cook has the potential to move ahead of Indian great Sachin Tendulkar as the world's all-time leading test run-scorer, England head coach Trevor Bayliss has said.

headline.print_headline: Bayliss Backs England's Cook to Surpass Tendulkar's Run Tally
